Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.69,0:00:42.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.95,0:00:47.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.94,0:00:49.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来得好早啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.54,0:00:51.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是球拍？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.09,0:00:53.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.98,0:00:59.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这球拍 是上周过生日时学长送我的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.14,0:01:02.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我让他教我网球
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.82,0:01:05.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦哦 进展顺利嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.74,0:01:09.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还停留在隔着玻璃吻着玩的阶段呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.83,0:01:10.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.99,0:01:13.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光是隔着玻璃的吻
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.55,0:01:16.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会在这种地方留下吻痕的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.29,0:01:18.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.20,0:01:22.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…你们已经把能做的都做了？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.59,0:01:24.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还没啦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.59,0:01:26.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.23,0:01:27.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.86,0:01:32.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学长问我下周日要不要去他家
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.51,0:01:33.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去…去他家？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.67,0:01:37.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃 说是想把我介绍给他父母
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.67,0:01:38.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么想
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.98,0:01:39.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.10,0:01:43.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉这是当天去男朋友家后
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.14,0:01:47.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,双亲突然有急事出门
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.31,0:01:51.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实质上是两人独处的模式
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.91,0:01:54.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.57,0:01:57.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像很开心
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.68,0:01:59.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真羡慕
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.02,0:02:02.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渡边同学不是结婚了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.94,0:02:05.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丈夫又不是男朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.56,0:02:09.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是要有男朋友才是学园生活嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.74,0:02:12.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以抱歉了 和子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.83,0:02:17.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下周日 没法跟和子去玩了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.72,0:02:19.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们约过吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.00,0:02:23.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你啊 忘了自己的生日吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.30,0:02:26.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.62,0:02:28.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 早
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.72,0:02:30.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.16,0:02:31.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.41,0:02:35.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早…
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//---------------------------------TXTA------------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.06,0:04:15.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有男朋友的午休啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.11,0:04:18.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像很好吃啊 哈密瓜包
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.16,0:04:24.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.56,0:04:27.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次请你吃更好吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.49,0:04:30.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下周日空出来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.41,0:04:33.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你过生日吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.34,0:04:35.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来须方家庆祝吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.32,0:04:41.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么那么 要开始做什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.58,0:04:44.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手作蛋糕是不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.44,0:04:46.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咖喱倒是没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.77,0:04:50.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主角就坐下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.05,0:04:56.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男士穿围裙的样子也很不错啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.14,0:04:59.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拓人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.68,0:05:02.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初中时有交往的女生吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.46,0:05:05.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没交往过啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.71,0:05:08.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是有喜欢的人吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.12,0:05:10.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么会这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.37,0:05:11.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你很受欢迎吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.02,0:05:14.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定有不少女孩子为你流泪吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.37,0:05:15.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.52,0:05:19.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.46,0:05:21.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洋葱给辣的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.82,0:05:26.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好棒 第一次看到须方君哭
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.67,0:05:31.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找浩史借的数码相机
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.15,0:05:34.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然在这种地方派上了用场
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.49,0:05:37.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拍下了贵重的一张
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.33,0:05:37.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.98,0:05:42.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你身为食客 还真大胆啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.79,0:05:46.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.24,0:05:48.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,炒洋葱还太早了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.08,0:05:53.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该先炒胡萝卜之类难熟的才对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.19,0:05:56.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么整个放进去了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.91,0:05:58.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶的洋葱
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.01,0:06:01.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是让无辜人士流泪的报应
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.49,0:06:03.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.53,0:06:06.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把洋葱整个扔进锅的那一刻
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.46,0:06:08.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就已经有罪了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.51,0:06:09.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才没
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.13,0:06:13.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)\pos(424,470)}你这个人还挺感情用事的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.76,0:06:15.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(424,470)}就算不是生日
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.20,0:06:20.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三人一起过周日感觉就像做梦一样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.30,0:06:23.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真希望是梦的话就不要醒了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.79,0:06:26.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再来一碗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.68,0:06:27.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.59,0:06:29.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.76,0:06:31.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没问题吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.31,0:06:32.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都第四碗了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.88,0:06:34.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是很好吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.97,0:06:35.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.74,0:06:37.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.35,0:06:39.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有 这个
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.95,0:06:42.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这怀表是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.90,0:06:46.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火灾把房间都烧掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.13,0:06:48.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以现在没钱
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.19,0:06:50.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今年的礼物就用这凑合一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.02,0:06:58.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个人 好像是我妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.21,0:07:02.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是很重要的怀表吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.11,0:07:06.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以想送给你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.07,0:07:09.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望和子以后能留着它
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.86,0:07:17.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,须方呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.95,0:07:20.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没送过礼物
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.25,0:07:23.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有这份心就够了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.79,0:07:25.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.78,0:07:27.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,须方的礼物
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.83,0:07:28.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这个
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.93,0:07:32.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…你几时拿走的？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.66,0:07:39.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是须方为了保护和子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.17,0:07:41.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从小一直带在身上的刀
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.21,0:07:50.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是须方的真心
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.11,0:08:02.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,旧怀表和危险的刀
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.51,0:08:04.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是差劲的礼物啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.53,0:08:08.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过是最棒的礼物
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.58,0:08:10.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.25,0:08:11.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会好好珍惜的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.52,0:08:16.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 上街玩去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.72,0:08:20.27,INCN4,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}柔和阳光下 绽开的蓓蕾
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.95,0:08:27.59,INCN4,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}小睡之中 感受着喜悦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.93,0:08:35.18,INCN4,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}任何人 一定都会面带微笑
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.36,0:08:42.62,INCN4,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}将它和过去的自己重叠
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.82,0:08:49.80,INCN4,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}触到了觉醒的勇气
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.91,0:08:56.05,INCN4,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}好似初始的清晨
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.29,0:09:00.84,INCN4,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}心逐渐融化
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.97,0:09:04.46,INCN4,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}在季节中等待
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.57,0:09:08.11,INCN4,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}大地上浮现出
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.19,0:09:11.86,INCN4,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}树叶间撒落的光影
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.95,0:09:15.39,INCN4,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}遍地的花朵
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.48,0:09:19.11,INCN4,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}是升空的光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.19,0:09:22.56,INCN4,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}数亿的生息
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.65,0:09:29.60,INCN4,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\blur4}此刻 世界转世重生
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.66,0:08:28.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\b0}（这是让无辜人士流泪的报应 洋葱）
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.82,0:08:32.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\b0}（抱歉哦 抱歉）
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.45,0:09:05.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小煌 你看那个
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.31,0:09:11.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很适合南方阳光的三人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.37,0:09:15.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甜品要点什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.27,0:09:22.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个嘛 今天想要刺激点的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.83,0:09:32.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是我打工的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.36,0:09:35.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.48,0:09:43.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是几位点的饮料
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.39,0:09:48.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请慢用
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.06,0:09:50.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.66,0:09:58.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我失陪一下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.69,0:10:00.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.09,0:10:03.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要问女孩子这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.12,0:10:05.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.56,0:10:09.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,机会来了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.95,0:10:12.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,窗华也可以一起来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.04,0:10:20.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,透过这针孔看着就行了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.21,0:10:23.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快 要和我牵手
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.11,0:10:32.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 透视能力好好玩
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.61,0:10:34.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你选哪个
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.66,0:10:39.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个嘛 还是活力少年吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.55,0:10:42.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我选小酷哥
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.94,0:10:44.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那开始咯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.37,0:10:45.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.71,0:10:48.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Qophlite（针孔）第一阶段
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.69,0:10:51.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,针之穴
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.75,0:11:05.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惠都
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.12,0:11:09.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不再唱歌了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.43,0:11:11.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么问
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.01,0:11:14.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久没在卡拉ok唱歌
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.08,0:11:18.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然想起以前一起唱歌的往事了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.41,0:11:20.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.36,0:11:21.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.05,0:11:28.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不会跟任何人说的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.51,0:11:31.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.30,0:11:33.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.29,0:11:36.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.53,0:11:43.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的帮我保密了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.37,0:11:54.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小煌？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.57,0:11:56.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.14,0:11:59.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小煌的第一阶段真有意思呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.67,0:12:02.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是第一次转移到男孩身上哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.15,0:12:07.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 是男孩呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.16,0:12:11.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.57,0:12:20.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,俺也去趟厕所
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.51,0:12:22.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,俺？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.88,0:12:34.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哟
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.42,0:12:41.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天也好可爱啊 丹治惠都同学
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.43,0:12:46.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拓人君？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.36,0:12:49.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.57,0:12:53.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不讨厌我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.43,0:13:03.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.22,0:13:07.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你和外表一样正经？班长
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.13,0:13:11.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.30,0:13:23.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.59,0:13:28.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拓人君绝对不会在这种时候做这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.59,0:13:30.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是拓人君
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.25,0:13:33.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.07,0:13:36.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.46,0:13:39.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是第一阶段的陷阱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.56,0:13:42.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是绮罗星十字团的驭星者吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.38,0:13:46.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们也对须方君做了同样的事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.55,0:13:48.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快停止这无聊的把戏
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.83,0:13:50.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把他们俩还给我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.45,0:13:52.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你明白吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.12,0:13:56.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这身体是真正的津名志拓人的身体
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.55,0:13:58.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能下得了手…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.83,0:14:02.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是你还要继续玩弄
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.80,0:14:05.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我重要的朋友拓人君的身体
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.52,0:14:07.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就当场…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.52,0:14:08.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刺下去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.19,0:14:26.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这女孩 是来真的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.33,0:14:30.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.54,0:14:45.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要装成别人真不容易呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.60,0:14:47.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.28,0:14:48.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.11,0:14:54.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小煌？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.62,0:14:58.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们现在得到了Tauburn的印记
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.41,0:15:00.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.93,0:15:04.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过用这种方式掌握男孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.98,0:15:07.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反而很无聊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.71,0:15:09.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.61,0:15:14.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来素体的游戏不正面进攻就没意思了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.98,0:15:20.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两人的气味…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.62,0:15:24.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在楼顶
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.05,0:15:28.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.81,0:15:33.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们俩都没事吧
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//---------------------------------TXTB------------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.75,0:15:43.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是无孔不入啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.78,0:15:46.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以为这次中招了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.21,0:15:48.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然占据身体
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.07,0:15:53.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难得能三人一起过我的生日
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.23,0:15:56.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绮罗星十字团最讨厌了！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.15,0:15:57.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那这样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.77,0:15:59.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难得的生日
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.51,0:16:01.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去吃蛋糕换换心情吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.31,0:16:17.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是 好不烦人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.45,0:16:19.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绮罗星十字团
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.74,0:16:27.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贵介公子 一刀两断
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.30,0:16:31.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,银河美少年
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.55,0:16:33.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Qophlight（针孔）
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.96,0:16:41.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近几次登场镜头被她们独占
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.29,0:16:44.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驯化
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.03,0:17:19.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飒爽登场
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.30,0:17:24.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,银河美少年
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.02,0:17:29.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Tauburn
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.07,0:17:34.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星剑 猫眼石
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.60,0:17:40.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星剑 翡翠
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.47,0:17:46.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星剑 蓝宝石
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.34,0:17:57.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先前失礼了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.59,0:18:00.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过男孩子的身体
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.87,0:18:02.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各种有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.11,0:18:05.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是段难得的体验
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.34,0:18:07.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才那家伙吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.28,0:18:09.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被如何了？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.28,0:18:11.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是她吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.67,0:18:20.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身体被擅自摆布 生气了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.84,0:18:24.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可饶恕的是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.53,0:18:27.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搅了和子的生日！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.31,0:18:35.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,华丽的登场只是噱头吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.25,0:18:40.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,银河之光啊 集于此身
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.83,0:18:44.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闪耀流星
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.15,0:18:49.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,变形？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.94,0:18:56.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.95,0:19:00.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去吧 用你的针贯穿他
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.27,0:19:01.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贯穿Tauburn
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.85,0:19:02.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好快
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.82,0:19:04.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在的我是蜂
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.01,0:19:07.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能躲过我的蛰刺吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.67,0:19:19.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战斗时 高处的一方有压倒性优势
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.29,0:19:22.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,致命的一刺
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.26,0:19:27.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能搞定的这种感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.53,0:19:29.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,意味着能搞定是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.83,0:19:31.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Tauburn
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.99,0:19:35.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,百褶喷射！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.60,0:19:46.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.68,0:19:52.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Tauburn…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.56,0:19:53.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飞了…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.82,0:20:01.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好快
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.16,0:20:21.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 咬住了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.63,0:20:26.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,银河之光啊 集于此身
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.11,0:20:30.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闪耀流星
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.33,0:20:37.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Tau飞弹
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.47,0:21:02.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.87,0:21:05.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好棒～Tauburn
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.38,0:21:08.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让人激动
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.29,0:21:20.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,津名志拓人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.64,0:21:22.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超乎想象的实力
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.75,0:21:27.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让窗华兴奋到这种程度的男子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.97,0:21:29.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是第一个
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.85,0:21:32.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生日快乐
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.86,0:21:34.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.37,0:21:36.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天不能陪你 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.79,0:21:39.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心意领了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.65,0:21:41.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那边怎么样？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.66,0:21:43.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去学长家了？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.70,0:21:45.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.71,0:21:47.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.48,0:21:50.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的被介绍给父母了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.12,0:21:52.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,期待落空？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.53,0:21:54.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 那倒没有
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.08,0:21:59.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说明学长看重我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.66,0:22:01.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心里甜甜的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.71,0:22:04.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 那就好
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.90,0:22:10.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好啊 有男朋友才算是校园生活吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.76,0:22:13.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐 和子决定哪个了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.52,0:22:19.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和子
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.62,0:22:23.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这家伙 看来想好了？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.97,0:22:26.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保密
Comment: 0,0:00:00.20,0:00:00.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//---------------------------------NEXT------------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.76,0:23:59.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我寄人篱下
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.08,0:24:00.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打扫自不用说
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.78,0:24:02.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到的令人震惊的场景
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.74,0:24:05.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及被提及的 替身的过去
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.21,0:24:07.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集 驭星者
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.64,0:24:09.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,画中彩虹
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.50,0:24:11.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的银河已然闪耀
